== Overview ==
The SxD10 is the highest level of protection utilizing Scaven technology. It generates a shielding field that is almost impossible to penetrate, while improving upon the efficiency of the SxD8, taking it above and beyond any other defensive device.

== Where to Acquire ==
The SxD10 can only be found once per reset in Horus Temples in the North East quadrant of Gamma.
